{
  "AllowedHosts": "*",
  "DEVGIS":{
    "DBType":"MYSQL", //数据库类型 Access "OLEDB","ACCESS"， SQLServer : "MSSQL","MSSQLSERVER","SQLSERVER" MYSQL:"MYSQL" Oracle:"ORACLE" Postgresql:"POSTGRESQL","POSTGRES" 如果不能识别则认为是Access数据库
    "Tables":["t_test","t_role"],//手动配置开放的表，如果此项为空则使用数据库检索
